    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >闪退回来了！</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/41cba287aec83f9212bc98debeaf0125.poster.avif?t=1770388548\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/41cba287aec83f9212bc98debeaf0125.webm?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/41cba287aec83f9212bc98debeaf0125.mp4?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>高速遇到高风险的地方。无情的战斗、响亮的电子音乐和令人上瘾的肾上腺素刺激混合在一起，将赢家与输家区分开来。万有引力只不过是一个空话。 参加一场激动人心的正面交锋，直至结束！ 这是 <strong>FLASHOUT 3</strong> 的世界将带您和您的骑行达到绝对极限的地方！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/f5ecabbc3630f05c9d08abfe082cfabd.poster.avif?t=1770388548\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/f5ecabbc3630f05c9d08abfe082cfabd.webm?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/f5ecabbc3630f05c9d08abfe082cfabd.mp4?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FLASHOUT 3</strong> 为您提供超快的船只、循环、跳跃和突然的急转弯！在最令人印象深刻的科幻赛道上测试你的技能，尽量不要落后！但是，如果发生这种情况，请不要出汗！释放火箭、枪支、炸弹和地雷的力量，帮助您降低竞争水平！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/640adafcc93b5ea618a6b701610cf901.poster.avif?t=1770388548\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/640adafcc93b5ea618a6b701610cf901.webm?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/640adafcc93b5ea618a6b701610cf901.mp4?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>参加一场激动人心的正面交锋，直至结束！见证壮观的撞车事故、失败的痛苦和胜利的甜蜜滋味！但不要眨眼！一切都可以在一瞬间结束！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/99ef2f98e40555656923f7fd5ae054dc.poster.avif?t=1770388548\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/99ef2f98e40555656923f7fd5ae054dc.webm?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/99ef2f98e40555656923f7fd5ae054dc.mp4?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/de13a3f44c3e4225a2559d72aa1f5e41.webp?t=1770388548\" width=600 height=39 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&gt; 两个字符可供选择</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/049692ac8bc4e81efcea0990352a1bc9.poster.avif?t=1770388548\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/049692ac8bc4e81efcea0990352a1bc9.webm?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/049692ac8bc4e81efcea0990352a1bc9.mp4?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/17cd28f7634686ac02917a216cef15c9.poster.avif?t=1770388548\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/17cd28f7634686ac02917a216cef15c9.webm?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/17cd28f7634686ac02917a216cef15c9.mp4?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&gt; 分屏模式</strong></h2><br>一个永远不会过时的选项，但在许多游戏中都缺少这个模式。在一个显示器上与朋友一起玩游戏会很有趣！ FLASHOUT 3 支持水平和垂直分屏模式。选择最适合您的一种模式！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/77b172757f7580e00b0b489a06207842.poster.avif?t=1770388548\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/77b172757f7580e00b0b489a06207842.webm?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761870/extras/77b172757f7580e00b0b489a06207842.mp4?t=1770388548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&gt; 支持虚拟现实</strong></h2><br>FLASHOUT 3 通过 OpenXR 支持所有流行的 VR 耳机！戴上头盔，舒适地坐下，拿起游戏手柄，让自己完全沉浸在游戏中！<br><br>在 VR 模式下运行游戏之前，请确保打开耳机。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&gt; 支持运动模拟器</strong></h2><br>FLASHOUT 3 是市场上第一款支持运动模拟器的 AG 赛车类游戏！系好安全带，用自己的身体感受速度、旋转和循环！戴上您的 VR 头盔，尽情体验 FLASHOUT 3！<br><br>该游戏支持与 Sim Racing Studio（最新测试版）兼容的模拟器和 Motion Systems () 的运动模拟器。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&gt; 美妙的电子音乐</strong></h2><br>FLASHOUT 3 有由著名的演示艺术家专门为游戏创作的高节奏电子音乐！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&gt; 还有什么？</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>由 10 场比赛组成的具有挑战性的战役；<br></li><li>不同的竞赛模式，包括标准竞赛、淘汰模式、毁灭模式等等！<br></li><li>八艘详细且超快的 AG 舰艇！<br></li><li>一个强大的武器库，助你一臂之力！<br></li><li> 10 个主题独特的电路，有两个版本 - 标准和反向！<br></li><li>令人惊叹的 3D 图形！<br></li><li>提供对游戏手柄的支持！<br></li><li>空气刹车系统！<br></li><li>还有更多！</li></ul>",
